2014年10月28日，{{le|TBS (電視頻道)|TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS}}預訂了由《[[每日秀|每日秀]]》銀幕夫妻檔[[傑森·瓊斯|傑森·瓊斯]]與[[薩曼莎·比|薩曼莎·比]]開創的電視試播集。<ref name="Pilot">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/jason-jones-samantha-bee-vacation-comedy-pilot-tbs-864065/|title=Jason Jones & Samantha Bee Vacation Comedy Gets TBS Pilot Order|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-10-28|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925064151/https://deadline.com/2014/10/jason-jones-samantha-bee-vacation-comedy-pilot-tbs-864065/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=presspilot>{{cite press release|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/10/28/tbs-orders-comedy-pilot-from-jason-jones-and-samantha-bee-235413/20141028tbs01/ |title=TBS Orders Comedy Pilot from Jason Jones & Samantha Bee |publisher=[[富頓評論家|富頓評論家]] |date=2014-10-28 |author={{le|TBS (電視頻道)|TBS (U.S. TV channel)|TBS}} | accessdate= 2016-03-25}}</ref>故事靈感是來自夫妻倆的家庭旅遊經驗，而劇中這一趟意外的家庭公路之旅，將會是一場不間斷的災難。<ref name="Pilot"/><ref name="Zea"/><ref>{{cite press release|url= http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2015/03/05/samantha-bee-heading-to-tbs-former-daily-show-correspondent-signs-up-to-host-comedy-series-269210/20150305tbs01/ |title=Samantha Bee Heading to TBS - Former "Daily Show" Correspondent Signs Up to Host Comedy Series |publisher=富頓評論家|date=2015-03-05 |author=TBS | accessdate= 2016-03-25}}</ref>劇情-{欲}-傳遞不管多麼逼近抓狂、不安穩的情勢，抑或是陌生人的介入，都能使一家人團聚在一起。<ref name="Pilot"/>倘若本劇成功成為一系列，每季故事將會記錄不同的旅途。<ref name="Pilot"/>

2015年2月24日，TBS宣布給予本劇系列預訂10集，預計於下季展開製作，瓊斯與薩曼莎將擔任執行製作，並由《[[扭轉時光機|扭轉時光機]]》、《{{le|昨夜風流|About Last Night (2014 film)}}》{{link-en|史蒂夫·平克|Steve Pink}}執導試播集。<ref name="Series Order Deadline">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/jason-jones-samantha-bee-tbs-comedy-series-pickup-1201380337/|title=Jason Jones & Samantha Bee’s TBS Comedy Pilot Picked Up To Series|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2015-02-24|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019164536/https://deadline.com/2015/02/jason-jones-samantha-bee-tbs-comedy-series-pickup-1201380337/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Series Order Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/samantha-bee-jason-jones-tbs-comedy-series-order-1201440378/|title=TBS Greenlights Comedy Series From ‘The Daily Show’s’ Samantha Bee & Jason Jones|publisher=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|author=Elizabeth Wagmeister|date=2015-02-24|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511170736/https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/samantha-bee-jason-jones-tbs-comedy-series-order-1201440378/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年4月6日，TBS在本劇開播前率先預訂第2季。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/the-detour-renewed-season-2-tbs-jason-jones-1201747278/|title=TBS Renews Jason Jones Comedy ‘The Detour’ For Season 2 Ahead of Series Debut|last=Wagmeister|first=Elizabeth|website=綜藝雜誌|access-date=2016-04-07|archive-date=2019-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926163903/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/the-detour-renewed-season-2-tbs-jason-jones-1201747278/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年4月25日，TBS宣布續訂第3季。<ref name="Season 3">{{Cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/the-detour-renewed-season-3-tbs-1202394649/|title=‘The Detour’ Renewed for Season 3 at TBS|author=Joe Otterson|website=綜藝雜誌|date=2017-04-25|accessdate=2017-04-25|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015355/https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/the-detour-renewed-season-3-tbs-1202394649/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月11日，TBS宣布續訂第4季。<ref name="Season 4">{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/the-detour-renewed-fourth-season-tbs-jason-jones-samantha-bee-1202388307/|title=‘The Detour’ Renewed For Fourth Season By TBS|author=Denise Petski|website=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|date=2018-05-11|accessdate=2018-05-11|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031829/https://deadline.com/2018/05/the-detour-renewed-fourth-season-tbs-jason-jones-samantha-bee-1202388307/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 選角 ===

傑森·瓊斯除開創本劇外，亦擔綱主演，飾演將與妻子和兩個孩子在前往[[基韋斯特_(佛羅里達州)|基韋斯特]]的路上，於車內展開24小時長途冒險的父親納特。<ref name="Pilot"/>2014年12月2日，宣布{{link-en|娜塔莉·姿雅|Natalie Zea}}將首次擔綱喜劇女主角，飾演納特的妻子蘿蘋。<ref name="Zea">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/natalie-zea-cast-jason-jones-samantha-bee-vacation-pilot-tbs-1201306464/|title=Natalie Zea To Star In Jason Jones & Samantha Bee’s TBS Vacation Pilot|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-12-02|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020061139/https://deadline.com/2014/12/natalie-zea-cast-jason-jones-samantha-bee-vacation-pilot-tbs-1201306464/|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月5日，宣布《[[我兒子是惡魔|凱文怎麼了？]]》艾希莉·吉拉瑟莫維奇與《[[外星鄰居|來自星星的鄰居]]》連恩·卡羅爾加入演出陣容，分別飾演叛逆、強勢的女兒蒂萊菈，以及慢半拍又對性知識不了解的兒子，亦是蒂萊菈孿生弟弟的傑瑞德。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/true-detective-cast-ronnie-gene-blevins-emily-ross-1201309672/|title=‘True Detective’ Adds Ronnie Gene Blevins, Emily Rios & Timothy V. Murphy; TBS Vacation Pilot Adds 2|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-12-05|accessdate=2017-04-26|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031104133/https://deadline.com/2014/12/true-detective-cast-ronnie-gene-blevins-emily-ross-1201309672/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

